CardData.FlavorText: The ceaseless attacks by the surrounding foes cause you to ignore navigation in favor of defense. With your attention on keeping yourselves alive rather than choosing your way down the mighty Anduin, you find that you have drifted into a closed channel. You will have to backtrack your course in order to free yourselves.

Localization.Title: Forced Off-course
Localization.Text: Restore every Objective to its full Quest value; then add +2 to each
